column2: Cannae Holdings, Inc. engages in the management and operation of a group of companies and investments. The company is headquartered in Las Vegas, Nevada and currently employs 26,413 full-time employees. The firm has investments in a variety of industries including Restaurants, Technology Enabled Healthcare Services, Financial Services and more. The firm holds majority and minority equity investment stakes in a number of entities, including Ceridian Holdings, LLC, American Blue Ribbon Holdings, and LLC and T-System Holding LLC.
